This paper discusses privacy-preserving and secure storage for personal data, which falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR) and database systems (cs.DB). The paper also discusses access control mechanisms, which can be categorized under cybernetics (cs.CY), social and information networks (cs.SI), and distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC).
